value: 8 10th Street Illegal Short-Term Rentals. Ongoing Illegal Short-Term Rentals by Lesses resulting in quality of life complaints from long-term residents. Host eventually provided proof of no pending reservations after repeat request by OSTR and Property Managment. https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/21553816.
